		<RichText x="738" y="255" width="439" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">疾叶化身标记玩家，在原地进行吟唱，并在标记处产生爆炸，爆炸产生额外的2道振波，这些都造成<span color="#99ff85">90%,22.5%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">疾叶化身释放一枚魔咒，坠落在玩家处并留下毒化迷雾，迷雾持续造成<span color="#99ff85">20%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="703" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">疾叶化身朝玩家方向蓄力，迸发草元素脉冲，造成<span color="#99ff85">70%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="927" width="437" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">疾叶化身即刻展开<span textDecoration="underline">试炼领域</span><span>，并获得</span><span textDecoration="underline">白护盾</span><span>，从领域内不断产生向外的互相垂直的4道亡蓟涟漪，造成</span><span color="#99ff85">50%</span><span>伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>，重复3回，最后收回领域并产生旋蔓崩破，造成</span><span color="#99ff85">100%</span><span>伤害，所剩的护盾将转为等量</span><span textDecoration="underline">悬木之灵御</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
